<a href="/articles/19890.html" class="com-grid-banner-article normal" >
	<div class="grid-banner-article-hd">
		<div class="imgcover">
				<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/19890/relatedMediumPc2/19890.jpg?1451360918" alt="腾讯给《热血传奇》手游拍了个微电影，还放进了朋友圈里">
		</div>

		<p class="category">
				<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/54/medium/54.png?1418161513" alt="游戏">
				<span>游戏</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-banner-article-bd clearfix">
		<div class="title-ribbon">
			<h1>腾讯给《热血传奇》手游拍了个微电影，还放进了朋友圈里</h1>
			<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-30 07:02:54 +0800"></span>
			<div class="ribbon">
